### Problem17

Look at the following program:

```java
public class Flow
{
    public static void main(String[]args)
    {
        int x = Integer.parseInt(args[0]);
        if (x % 3 == 0)
        {
            if ( x % 2 ==0 && x <10 ) System.out.println(1);
            else System.out.println(2);
        }
        else
        {
            if (x!=20) System.out.println(3);
            if (x >15) System.out.println(4);
        }
    }
}
